  "description": {
    "en": [
      "The 228-piece LONDY Magic Building set offers a larger fort kit with four rod lengths and red-yellow connector balls.",
      "PP parts are marked for ages 5+ and support wider forts, taller towers, and open-ended building layouts.",
      "Packed set price is $34.11, with about 3.7 kg quoted weight. Packing is color box with outer carton.",
      "OEM packaging is available for private-label orders."
    ],
    "zh": [
      "228件 LONDY Magic Building 是更大规格的堡垒套装，配置四种杆长和红黄连接球。",
      "PP 配件标注适用 5 岁以上，可搭建更宽的堡垒、更高的塔形和更自由的结构。",
      "单盒合计价格 $34.11，报价重量约 3.7 kg；包装为彩盒加外箱。",
      "支持贴牌订单的 OEM 包装。"
    ]
  },
